If you remember my last tutorial or lesson,

00:05:31.610 --> 00:05:37.985
you might remember that line height for heading is almost 100 percent or 110 percent,

00:05:37.985 --> 00:05:40.590
so it's closer to 100 percent.

00:05:41.210 --> 00:05:49.865
You can see I am using these three lines over here to balance this heading.

00:05:49.865 --> 00:05:54.710
You can see I am using these three lines,

00:05:54.710 --> 00:05:59.190
so let's align it a bit more at the down.

00:05:59.540 --> 00:06:04.700
Let's have the size of this one equal to 20 pixels,

00:06:04.700 --> 00:06:06.230
so it is easily readable.

